Case: Nadine-Robinson-Premise-12-19-2020
Client: Nadine Robinson

Aaron Whaley confirmed the communication with Nadine Robinson regarding her pending premises liability case and the current status of her claim.
Recap
Aaron Whaley contacted Nadine Robinson to discuss her premises liability case from December 19, 2020, and assess the current progress.
Nadine provided Aaron with updates on her case and expressed her continued interest in pursuing the matter.
Tasks
Aaron needs to review the case file and determine the next steps for Nadine's premises liability claim.
episodes.natural_language:
On December 19, 2020, Aaron Whaley contacted Nadine Robinson to discuss her pending premises liability case and to assess the current progress of her claim. He also confirmed the communication with Nadine regarding the case and the current status of her claim.

During the conversation, Nadine provided updates on her case and expressed her continued interest in pursuing the matter.

The tasks identified are for Aaron to review the case file and determine the next steps for Nadine’s premises liability claim.
